divs: Sighting DetailsIt all started when i was at stanges park in Merrill,Wisconsin. I was sitting next to some bushes with one of my friends. Then all of a sudden I saw some weird oval shaped object flying across the sky at what seemed to be a low rate of speed considering it had a really low humming sound coming from it, but it might of sounded like that because it was going so fast. All i know is that I'm pretty damn sure it wasn't a plane, because what i heard was probably louder then a train. It sounded as loud as being right in front of a train when the whistle blows when it comes by, but a really low humming noise. I thought it would have been bigger then it looked cause it was so loud, but i guess not. I can also verify that there were red, white and blue lights flashing in an odd pattern that I saw the last time i sighted a UFO. I lost sight of the object when it got out of view behind the tree line.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Merrill
There were no other sightings in Merrill on or around October 24th 2008
Summary: I saw an oval shaped object moving across the sky very slowly and it was making a very low humming sound
